de.feig.FEDM.Core.TagHandler

Class TH_ISO15693_KSW

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.feig.FEDM.Core.TagHandler.TH_Base
      • de.feig.FEDM.Core.TagHandler.TH_ISO15693
        • de.feig.FEDM.Core.TagHandler.TH_ISO15693_KSW

  • public class TH_ISO15693_KSW
extends TH_ISO15693
    Base class for ISO15693 transponder of manufacturer KSW Microtec GmbH.
    This class supports addressed, non-addressed and selected mode in Host-Mode
    .
    Description:
    High-level class for easy-to-use Transponder specific communication. See ITagGroup for additional information.
    All methods are similiar to specific commands of KSW. Thus, you must refer to the Technical Datasheets to get detailed information about the methods and the parameters.
    Secondly, all methods of this class are Custom specific commands, realized with the Reader command [0xB1], which are described in the Application Note KSW Custom and Proprietary Commands.pdf

    Note: Programmers should be familiar with the ISO 15693 standard.
